reviewText:
Simple instruction here, but ok for the intermediate.
Step be step movement details would make for a better more learnable format.
Excellent video by an incredible instructor. He shows the essence of true no nonsense WSL Wing Chun. I await his next DVD.
Very well done . Wing Chun basic concepts explained by a teacher who knows his wing Chun . I really enjoyed it . This shouldn't be watched once but again and again .
